"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61945","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2014-06-19","<p /> <p /> <p>The number of Independent Living Fund users recorded as having autism, Asperger's syndrome or a learning disability with autism as their main condition is currently 332.</p>",,"Lord Freud",,"2014-06-19T14:43:50.2529975Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61945/answer","Biography information for Lord Freud","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61945/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61945/answer",,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2014-06-16","Independent Living Fund: Autism","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty's Government, further to the Written Answer by Lord Freud on 11 June (WA 7), how many people in receipt of Independent Living Fund payments have autism as their main condition.","false","Biography information for Baroness Uddin",,"Baroness Uddin","HL363"
