"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62112","Ministry of Justice","false","2014-06-20","<p /> <p /> <p>Women should be given any items required to meet essential personal needs for their first 24 hours in custody, including toiletries, clean clothing and a towel. Women also must have easy access to a choice of sanitary provision. Tampons with applicators must be one of the choices.</p><p> </p><p>All prisons across the female custodial estate provide Interlude tampons and sanitary towels to women free of charge. Other brands of sanitary products are available for women to buy via the National Product list.</p>","Bermondsey and Old Southwark","Simon Hughes",,"2014-06-20T14:34:15.8877369Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62112/answer","Biography information for Simon Hughes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62112/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62112/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2014-06-16","Prisoners: Sanitary Protection","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, whether a full range of sanitary products is provided free-of-charge to female prisoners.","false","Biography information for Fiona Mactaggart","Slough","Fiona Mactaggart","200773"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62113","Ministry of Justice","false","2014-06-18","<p /> <p /> <p>Female prisoners can purchase the following sanitary products from the National Product List:</p><p>Sanitary pads—Always Ultra Normal 32s—price £2.69</p><p>Sanitary towels—Tena Lady Normal 12s—price £2.69.</p>","Bermondsey and Old Southwark","Simon Hughes",,"2014-06-18T11:01:49.0128746Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62113/answer","Biography information for Simon Hughes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62113/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62113/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2014-06-16","Prisoners: Sanitary Protection","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, which types and brands of sanitary products female prisoners may purchase from the National Product List; and at what cost.","false","Biography information for Fiona Mactaggart","Slough","Fiona Mactaggart","200774"
